  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Chronic pancreatitis patient selected for total pancreatectomy and islet
             autotransplantation.

          2. Age between 18-69.

        Exclusion Criteria:

        1. Had prior pancreatic surgeries.

        Note: The study was initially designed only to enroll diabetes free patients. To increase
        enrollment, we extended the inclusion criteria by allowing patients who are pre-diabetic to
        participate the study. This revision was approved by the MUSC IRB on 11/10/2015.
      </textblock>
